videos.description: Tre Jones feeds Zion Williamson on the baseline and he explodes for a powerhouse dunk early in the first half vs. Hartford.
videos.headline: Williamson gets up for powerful two-handed flush

videos.description: Duke forward Javin DeLaurier pokes away a Hartford pass and takes it all the way for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: DeLaurier steals and slams

videos.description: John Carroll drives baseline and goes up against Zion Williamson, sinking a layup and earning a trip to the foul line.
videos.headline: Hartford's Carroll draws and-1 on Zion

videos.description: Tre Jones grabs a rebound off a Hartford miss and goes coast-to-coast to scoop in a layup.
videos.headline: Duke's Jones scoops and scores in transition

videos.description: Cam Reddish steals and passes to RJ Barrett for a wide-open 3-pointer vs. Hartford.
videos.headline: Reddish feeds Barrett for transition 3

videos.description: Zion Williamson steals a pass and jams a wide-open dunk, making Cameron Indoor Stadium erupt.
videos.headline: Zion throws down electric two-handed slam

videos.description: Tre Jones passes to freshman RJ Barrett, who drives the lane and hammers down a one-handed dunk vs. Hartford.
videos.headline: Barrett rises up over defender

videos.description: Zion Williamson dunks in transition, then tosses a pass off the backboard to RJ Barrett for a two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Zion, Barrett jam back-to-back dunks

videos.description: Hartford guard J.R. Lynch drives to the hoop, but Zion Williamson swats his layup attempt in the second half.
videos.headline: Zion spikes Hartford layup off backboard
